releaseNotes:
1.0.0: First version of EventSource Event doc generator, handles cases where CustomEventSource is directly derived from EventSource class, rather than Interface deriving from EventSource.
          1.0.1: Fixing Output csv file to be placed at OutDir
          Note: only supports .Net4.5
summary: This MSBuild task generates documentation for Events in a ETW EventSource class. This can combine event method comments like summary and resolution to helps Operations take action on the events.
title: ETW EventSource Events Document (csv) generator.
